---
name: draft-substack
description: Draft a Substack Note (300 char limit, warm subscriber-aware tone)
triggers:
  - draft a substack note
  - write a substack update
  - post to substack
  - substack note
---

Read the skill file at `.postlane/commands/draft-substack.md`, then draft one Substack Note. Output sets `platforms: ["substack_notes"]` in `meta.json`.
